data.description: Check out this gorgeous Desert View Resale in pristine condition in between Horizon City and the Far East! Seller has an 2.25% assumable Va loan! Offering over 2300 square feet of livable space, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a LOFT! Living areas are open concept and perfect for hosting guests. Kitchen offers granite countertops, ceramic tile backsplash and a stainless steel appliance package. The primary bedroom is located on the first floor, while the other 3 secondary bedrooms are on level two. Backyard is a great size and a blank canvas for you to create your own personal oasis! Schedule your showing today! Seller will consider a rent to own option.
